        h2 Welcome to VizSec 2008
      p The 5th International Workshop on Visualization for Cyber Security was held in Cambridge, MA USA on September 15, 2008. VizSec brought together researchers and practitioners in information visualization and security to address the specific needs of the cyber security community through new and insightful visualization techniques. The keynote speaker was <a href='http://www.cs.umd.edu/~ben/'>Ben Shneiderman</a>.
      p VizSec was held in conjunction with the <a href='http://www.ll.mit.edu/RAID2008/'>11th International Symposium on Recent Advances in Intrusion Detection (RAID)</a>.
      p The proceedings are in <a href="http://www.springeronline.com/978-3-540-85931-4">Springer Online</a> and <a href="http://www.springerlink.com/content/978-3-540-85931-4/">Springer Link</a>.

